Onload-8.0.0
============

 This is a major feature release of Onload.


Linux distribution support
--------------------------
 This package is supported on:
 - Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.6 - 7.8
 - Red Hat Enterprise Linux 8.1 - 8.2
 - SuSE Linux Enterprise Server 12 sp4 and sp5
 - SuSE Linux Enterprise Server 15 sp1 and sp2
 - Canonical Ubuntu Server LTS 18.04 and 20.04
 - Debian 9 "Stretch"
 - Debian 10 "Buster"
 - Linux kernels 4.4 - 5.7


sfc_affinity
------------

The deprecated support for adding steering filters through the sfc_affinity
driver and the sfcaffinity tool has been removed.
